California residents have the right not to receive discriminatory treatment by us for the exercise of their rights conferred by the California Consumer Privacy Act.
INFORMATION ABOUT CHILDREN
We will not knowingly collect or request personal information from children under 16 (or any other age stipulated by law applicable to your region). If you are under 16, please do not send your personal information to us, including but not limited to your name, address, phone number or email address. If you believe we may have any information about children under 16, you may send an email to legal@pixocial.com
(please quote “Passure” in your email title)
